            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "I'm going to close this, I think I can work around it in NumPy.\n\nIf you ever do add this optimization to Cython, you could also use the [`CO_OPTIMIZED`](https://docs.python.org/3/library/inspect.html#inspect.CO_OPTIMIZED) code object flag to emulate exactly what CPython does here.  See e.g. https://github.com/numpy/numpy/issues/30991#issuecomment-4046539714.",
